<br>
For starters, there are 3 dragons in WToV, all of which are killable by the Fed, if we were to work together on it. The easiest of these is Telki by far. Here are the Allakhazam links for them if you would like to see.<br>
Telk- <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=6468">eqbeastiary.allakhazam.co...ml?id=6468</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
