<br>
Secondly, Lendi is the one we are least likely to get a shot at for a while, as people farm her for ST keys, however Telki is almost always left up as the bigger guilds feel he isn't worth their time. <br>
<br>
Third, the faction hits are easy enough to fix. If you are concerned abtou your Yelinak faction, I managed to raise mine in from indiff to kindly (3 steps) in 3 hours of fighting in the Tormax area of Kael. Regular CoV faction hits are one step down (ie, from ally to warmly)....this can be fixed in a few hours in the arena of Kael.<br>
<br>
I don't expect many people to be interested at all, but I just thought I'd post it and see who has what to say. If we want to take down Vindicator, this is as good a place as any to start aquiring the items to do it with.<br>
<br>
